data.description: This spectacular 5 split level 4/BR, 2/2 bath new build 2023, Schottenstain home, at the new at Reserve at Northlake Woods community in Sunbury. This plan offers an island kitchen with pantry, lots of cabinet space, granite countertops and new SS Appliances.This home has two-story living room and dining with a lot of sunlight. First level open staircase provides a view to the upstairs loft. Primary Suite with private bath and walk-in closet has a tray ceiling. Additional 3 bedrooms and full bath in the upper level with the foyer.  Lower level family room has kitchen cabinets bar with the sink and the half bath, also has unfinished basement.Backyard has a water view to a cozy pondClose to the highway I-71, restaurants and shopping Centers. All furniture, Washer and dryer will stay.
